: - To write a MATLAB program to generate a random signal and plot the waveform
Apparatus Required: - PC with MATLAB 7.0
2)6713 dsk cc studio v3.1 software
3)Dsp processor kit
PROGRAM:
include<stdio.h>
main()
{
int max,i,N,n,sum=0,avg=0;
printf("enter the maximum range of the random sequence");
scanf("%d",&max);
printf("enter the number of random samples");
scanf("%d",&N);
for(i=0;i<N;i++)
{
n=rand()%max+1;
printf("\n%d",n);
sum=sum+n;
}
avg=sum/N;
printf("The mean value of random sequence is %d",avg);
}






OUTPUT:Enter the maximum range of the random sequence 150
Enter the number of random samples 6
39
59
64
116
2
78
The mean value of random sequence is 59
Result:A random sequence is generated by using c-program
